description:
Katherine Ryan is a Canadian comedian, writer, presenter, actress and singer.

She has appeared on many British panel shows, including as a regular team captain on 8 Out of 10 Cats and Never Mind the Buzzcocks, A League of Their Own, Mock the Week, Would I Lie to You?, QI, Just a Minute, Safeword, and Have I Got News for You.

She has over 920k followers on her Instagram.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
